v1 Features:
- Show join/leave messages
- Roster of users who are present
- New shard button; creates shortlink
- Change nickname button
- Prompt for nickname before joining (except for landing shard)
- URL auto-linking

Polish:
- Add a favicon static file
- See where app stats is spending time

